name: Corneo's Night Elf (World of Warcraft) embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding to generate night elves from World of Warcraft. Use corneo_night_elf to activate the embedding.

It was trained on NAI at clip skip 2, so will work best on NAI-derived anime models.

By itself it will tend towards flesh/pink-colored skin, so you may way to use something like purple_skin as well. I'm sure you could nudge it towards generating blood elves too.

Example images produced using AbyssOrangeMix2

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
